                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">员工体验 (EX)</h3>
                  <p>内部 Wiki、SOP、培训资料、内网。沉淀知识，加速入职。</p>
                </div>

                <div
                  class="bg-slate-50 border-l-8 border-slate-500 text-slate-700 p-6 rounded-r-xl shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-center"
                >
                  <div class="text-4xl font-black opacity-20 mb-2">BX</div>
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">品牌体验 (BX)</h3>
                  <p>官网、营销落地页、博客、全球化门户。统一品牌声音。</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Slide 5: Products -->
          <div class="swiper-slide">
            <div
